lead_paragraph: Australian Rod Pampling recovered from a poor start to take a one-shot lead in the second round of the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open in Las Vegas on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Aussie Pampling Cools Off but Maintains Lead in Las Vegas
